Package com.nathcat.messagecat_server

Class ListenRule

java.lang.Object
com.nathcat.messagecat_server.ListenRule
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class ListenRule extends Object implements Serializable
A listening rule to be supplied to a client when they want to listen for actions performed on the server by other clients.
